Recipe: Creamy Mushroom Herb Pasta
Servings: 4

Ingredients:
8 oz mushrooms 
12 oz fettuccine 
2 cloves garlic, minced
3 Tbsp butter 
3 Tbsp all-purpose flour 
1.5 cups vegetable broth 
3 sprigs fresh thyme (or 1/4 tsp dried)
1 tsp rubbed sage 
1/2 cup half and half 
Salt and pepper to taste 

